== 概要 ==
This template provides a citation for use with the population estimates held in the following templates:
* {{tl|English district population}}
* {{tl|English district rank}}
* {{tl|English district density}}
* {{tl|English district density rank}}
* {{tl|English cerem counties}}
* {{tl|English admin counties}}
* {{tl|Welsh council population}}
* {{tl|Scottish council populations}}
* {{tl|NI district population}}.  

The year to which they relate (currently {{United Kingdom statistics year}}) is held as {{tl|United Kingdom statistics year}}.  An optional parameter '''area''' produces instead a citation for the source of district area measurements, held in the following templates (and as parameters in the Welsh, Scottish and Northern Irish templates mentioned above):
* {{tl|English district area}}
* {{tl|English district area rank}}

Where the population citation varies per country add an optional parameter of the country, '''England''', '''NI''', '''Scotland''' or '''Wales'''.

== 參數及使用方法 ==
===人口===
Place the template where you would normally include a citation template.  You need to include the <nowiki><ref> ...</ref></nowiki> markup (this allows you to name the reference).  Example:

:<nowiki>Havering has a population of {{English district population|GSS=E09000016}} ({{United Kingdom statistics year}}).<ref>{{United Kingdom district population citation|England}}</ref></nowiki>

which will produce

:Havering has a population of {{English district population|GSS=E09000016}} ({{United Kingdom statistics year}}).

with a reference for England

:{{United Kingdom district population citation|England}}

=== 面積 ===
:<nowiki>Havering has an area of {{English district area|GSS=E09000016}}km².<ref>{{United Kingdom district population citation|area}}</ref></nowiki>

will produce

:Havering has an area of {{English district area|GSS=E09000016}}km².

with a reference

:{{United Kingdom district population citation|area}}

